"{\"uid\": \"morningstaronline.co.uk-article-french-police-accused-social-cleansing-ahead-olympics-through-evicting-refugee-camps\", \"text\": \"FRENCH police evicted refugees from a makeshift camp in Paris before dawn today, in what migrant rights groups say is a \\\"social cleansing\\\" campaign to spruce up the capital for this summer's Olympic Games.  About 30 teenage boys and young men, reportedly from west Africa, were woken before sunrise and ordered to pack their bags and tents before being moved.  \\\"I was already scared but I am even more scared because I do not know where to go,\\\" 16-year-old Boubacar Traore, who fled conflict in Burkina Faso, said.  ROGER McKENZIE explains how Ibrahim Traore has sparked the flames of hope across Africa, while the Western powers seek to extinguish all attempts to build true sovereignty in the long-exploited continent\"}"